data.description: Welcome to your serene countryside retreat! This beautifully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bath home sits on a sprawling 1-acre property, offering you the best of both worlds: tranquility and convenience. Step inside to discover a spacious, open-concept layout that effortlessly connects the large kitchen, dining area, and cozy living room. Enjoy granite countertops, tile and wood floors, and fully remodeled bathrooms for modern comfort. But the real magic happens outdoors. A long driveway leads you to a detached 2-car garage, ensuring ample parking and storage space. Enjoy family evenings on the covered patio or side balcony, surrounded by the beauty of mature trees and open space.  Storage enthusiasts will be delighted by the huge metal hangar, perfect for storing anything from cars to RVs. There's also an additional shed in the back for added convenience. With an extra slab ready for your creative touch, you can expand with a courtyard or sports court. Located just minutes from 1604 and a convenient commute to both Randolph AFB and Ft Sam Houston, this property offers the peace and privacy of country living while remaining close to the conveniences of San Antonio and NO HOA OR CITY TAXES. Embrace this unique opportunity for a harmonious blend of comfort, nature, and accessibility - your new home sweet home awaits!
